-- Erie Hires GE’s Postema as Insurer’s Chief Investment Officer
-- B y   D a n   K r a u t
-- 2012-06-05T12:16:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-05/erie-hires-ge-s-postema-as-insurer-s-chief-investment-officer.html
Erie Indemnity Co. (ERIE) , the seller of
life insurance and property-casualty coverage, hired Brad Postema as chief investment officer.  Postema joins from GE Asset Management where he was senior
portfolio manager for insurance, according to a PR Newswire
statement today from Erie, which is based in the Pennsylvania
city of the same name.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Dan Kraut in  New York  at 
